{
  "texts": [
    "Researchers should continue to investigate the synergies between AI, virtual reality, augmented reality, and other related fields to unlock the full potential of the Metaverse. 5.",
    "Emphasis on practical implementations: While academic research is valuable, it is also essential to focus on practical implementations of AI in the Metaverse.",
    "Researchers can collaborate with industry partners to explore real-world applications, address challenges, and bring innovative AI-driven experiences to users.",
    "It is worth noting that the topic of using AI in the Metaverse is relatively recent, as indicated by the statistics gathered from the Web of Science Core Collection.",
    "With 217 publications selected over the past 3 years, it is evident that researchers and academics are beginning to recognize the importance and potential of AI in shaping the future of the Metaverse."
  ]
}